cs.DL, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.SI, cs.CY

The paper discusses bibliometric analysis and the problem of missing author address information in the Web of Science database. Based on this, the most likely sub-category is cs.DL (Digital Libraries) as it deals with the organization, retrieval, and distribution of digital information. The paper also touches upon information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), social networks (cs.SI), and cybersecurity (cs.CY) as they relate to bibliometric analysis and research performance evaluation.
